'''邁克爾·艾倫·斯坦伯格'''（{{lang-en|Michael Alan Steinberg}}；{{bd|1959年|2月6日|}}），是一位美國[[律師|律師]]和[[政治家|政治家]]。他曾兩次參選[[佛罗里达州议会|佛罗里达州议会]]<ref>{{cite news|title=For a better state House Series: TIMES RECOMMENDS |publisher=St. Petersburg Times |date= August 23, 2002 |page=16A}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ELECTION RESULTS: [STATE / SUNCOAST Edition]|publisher=''St. Petersburg Times'' |date=September 7, 2006 |page=3B }}</ref>，又曾爭取[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統選舉]][[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]黨內提名<ref name=FECfiling>{{cite web |title=FEC filing: Michael Steinberg for President committee |url=http://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/521/13031141521/13031141521.pdf |publisher=FEC.gov |accessdate= |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111195901/https://docquery.fec.gov/pdf/521/13031141521/13031141521.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/the-fix/wp/2014/12/16/here-is-a-primer-to-people-other-than-jeb-bush-who-are-running-for-president-in-2016/ | title=Here is a primer on people other than Jeb Bush who are running for president in 2016 | work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] | date=December 16, 2014 | accessdate= | author=Fuller, Jaime | archive-date=2015-07-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702010323/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/the-fix/wp/2014/12/16/here-is-a-primer-to-people-other-than-jeb-bush-who-are-running-for-president-in-2016/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但均告失敗。後來他代表[[美国改革党|美国改革党]]作為[[洛基·德拉富恩特|洛基·德拉富恩特]]的副手，成為2016年美國總統選舉副總統候選人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thegreenpapers.com/G16/FL |title="The Green Papers: Florida 2016 General Election" |access-date=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226151957/https://www.thegreenpapers.com/G16/FL |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[[Richard_Winger|Winger, Richard]] (August 9, 2016) [http://ballot-access.org/2016/08/09/reform-party-nominates-rocky-de-la-fuente-for-president/ "Reform Party Nominates Rocky De La Fuente for President"] {{Wayback|url=http://ballot-access.org/2016/08/09/reform-party-nominates-rocky-de-la-fuente-for-president/ |date=20181023224015 }},  ''[[Ballot_Access_News|Ballot Access News]]''. Retrieved August 19, 2016.</ref>。

2010年他在[[美国社会安全保险|美国社会安全保险]]工作差不多30年時，被《[[坦帕灣時報|坦帕灣時報]]》稱為專家：「你會禍不單行」。他稱人口老齡化和經濟表現不佳是地方增加索賠的原因，2008年至2009年的全國記錄增長了21%；而當時他正在競選[[佛罗里达州众议院|佛罗里达州众议院]]第四十七選區議席<ref name=rise>{{cite news |url=http://www.tampabay.com/news/aging/socialsecurity/social-security-disability-claims-on-the-rise-in-tampa-bay/1122340 |title=Social Security disability claims on the rise in Tampa Bay |author=Kameel Stanley |date=September 17, 2010 |publisher=''[[Tampa_Bay_Times|Tampa Bay Times]]'' |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231053811/http://www.tampabay.com/news/aging/socialsecurity/social-security-disability-claims-on-the-rise-in-tampa-bay/1122340 |archivedate=2015年12月31日 }}</ref>。

